# Filenames - English Only (Global)

- **Default rule**: All filenames must use **English** (letters, numbers, hyphens, underscores).
- **Scope**: New files, renamed files, plans, docs, assets across all projects.
- **Format**: Use lowercase-with-hyphens or snake_case. Avoid spaces and non-ASCII.
- **Content**: File content may use any language. This rule applies only to **filenames**.
- **Examples**: `oneask-web-automation-tool.plan.md` not `oneask_网页自动化聚合工具.plan.md`
